Package mmj.tl

Class TheoremLoader

java.lang.Object
mmj.tl.TheoremLoader
public class TheoremLoader extends Object
The Theorem Loader facility's main control module.

Note: this class is primarily an entry point and convenience for Theorem Loader users (batch or GUI.)
